Title : 10th Golden Rooster Awards
Text : '''The 10th Golden Rooster Awards''' honoring the best in film of 1990, was given in Hongshan Gymnasium, [[Wuchang District|Wuchang]], [[Hubei Province]], December 10, 1990.<ref>[http://www.cnhubei.com/xwzt/2008zt/hbgg30y/dsj30y/200803/t254901_11.shtml 湖北30年大事记：1990年12月] cnhubei.com March 14, 2008</ref>

